  "plan": "## Amaretto GenePattern Module — Implementation Plan\n\n### 1. Overview\nAmaretto is a GenePattern module that Discovery of driver genes using epigenomic, genomic and transcriptomic data using module networks with penalized regression.\n\n### 2. Parameters\nThe module exposes 10 parameters:\n- Required: expression.file, number.of.modules, percent.genes, output.file, driver.gene.list, driver.gene.list.selection.mode, gene.sets.database\n- Optional: copy.number.file, methylation.file, driver.gene.list.file\n\n### 3. Command Line\n```\n/usr/bin/Rscript --no-save --quiet --slave --no-restore /usr/local/bin/amaretto/run_amaretto_module.R  --expression.file\\=<expression.file> --copy.number.file\\=<copy.number.file> --methylation.file\\=<methylation.file> --output.file\\=<output.file> --percent.genes\\=<percent.genes> --number.of.modules\\=<number.of.modules> --driver.gene.list\\=<driver.gene.list> --driver.gene.list.file\\=<driver.gene.list.file> --driver.gene.list.selection.mode\\=<driver.gene.list.selection.mode> --num.cpu\\=<job.cpuCount>  --gene.sets.database\\=<gene.sets.database>\n```\n\n### 4. Docker Image\nDocker image: genepattern/docker-amaretto\\:0.53\n\n### 5. Validation Strategy\n- Validate all required parameters are provided\n- Validate file formats match expected extensions\n- Check parameter value ranges where applicable\n\n### 6. Implementation Roadmap\nPhase 1: Wrapper script implementation\nPhase 2: Docker container setup\nPhase 3: Parameter validation and error handling\nPhase 4: Testing and documentation",
  "wrapper_script": "run_amaretto_module.R",
